            <span class="alicyn-lab-badge">Investigación</span>
            <span class="alicyn-lab-badge">Wellness celular</span>
            <span class="alicyn-lab-badge">Skin science</span>
            <span class="alicyn-lab-badge">Aesthetic Labs</span>
