        </article>
        <article class="alicyn-lab-trust-card">
          <svg class="alicyn-lab-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2 4 6v6c0 5 3.4 8.5 8 10 4.6-1.5 8-5 8-10V6l-8-4Z"/><path d="M9 12h6M12 9v6"/></svg>
          <strong>Aesthetic Labs</strong>
