          <p>Compara productos por eje de investigación o consulta una ruta antes de comprar.</p>
          <div class="alicyn-lab-actions">
            <a class="alicyn-lab-button" href="{{ section.settings.primary_button_link | default: '/collections/peptidos' }}">{{ section.settings.primary_button_label | escape }}</a>
            <a class="alicyn-lab-button alicyn-lab-button-secondary" data-lab-result-whatsapp target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://wa.me/{{ section.settings.whatsapp_number | default: '525542388056' }}">Hablar por WhatsApp</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
